<h2>English</h2>
Here, 3 informations are required:
<ul>
<li>First name</li>
<li>Last name</li>
<li>Date</li>
</ul>
All informations below, are not required.
<br>
<br>
However, Mail must be useful to sending the billing by mail. <br>
These informations are saved in RoomX database, into the table: guest.<br>
When check-in is done, if the guest is already in the database, you have this information: <i>Guest already exist, Check-in Done</i> . Like
that, you could know if it's a new client or not.<br><br>
